Name: Enionax
About the game: Enionax is sent back to 1980 — the dawning of video games — due to a mistake. A classic plateformer 2D game Help her come back to our time by going through the various levels/eras of platformers. You will have to walk through various supports to come back to our time in this platefomer 2D game . Assets A classic plateformer 2D game ! Revisit the various eras of video games with humour. Try to find out all the easter eggs in the game. Go through various gameplays as times change. Enjoy original music by Valentin Skorra.
